Shooters Island Shipyard Company v. Standard Shipbuilding Corporation; United States v. Standard Shipbuilding Corporation; and United States v. Standard Shipbuilding Corporation. Decided October 8, 1923. Mr. Alfred A. Wheat, Special Assistant to the Attorney General,- for petitioners.
